org.opendaylight.controller.sal.packet

Class RawPacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.sal.packet.RawPacket

  • public class RawPacket
extends java.lang.Object
    Describe a raw Data Packet, this is how a packet is received from the network and how it will be transmitted. It essentially wraps the raw bytestream
